<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Activate Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #4CAF50;
    }
    .activation-code {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #FF5722;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      border: 2px solid #ddd;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Account Activation</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for registering with us. To complete your account activation, please use the activation code below:</p>
    <div class="activation-code">
      <%= text %>
    </div>
    <p>This code will expire in 15 minutes, so be sure to use it soon!</p>
    <p>If you did not create an account with us, please ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>Your Company Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
